<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The situation seems to be that it is mathemati=
cally impossible for Bed Bath &amp; Beyond Inc. to raise enough money by se=
lling stock to avert bankruptcy. It=E2=80=99s not=C2=A0<em>quite=C2=A0</em>=
as simple as that =E2=80=94=C2=A0you can write down some scenarios where it=
=C2=A0<em>can=C2=A0</em>raise enough money =E2=80=94=C2=A0but they are pret=
ty far-fetched.=C2=A0The <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/31230764.264442/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9iZWQtYmF0aC1i=
